	<div class="container tour-block-padding">
		<h1>Add Your Guests</h1>
		<p>Add guests here and they will appear in the table below</p>
		<div class="form-horizontal row text-center" style="padding-top: 20px;">
			<div class="form-group has-feedback">
				{{mdl-textfield label='Name & Surname*' value=name}}
			</div>
			<div class="form-group has-feedback">
				{{mdl-textfield label='Email Address' value=email}}
			</div>
			<div class="form-group has-feedback">
				{{mdl-textfield label='Contact Number' value=cell}}
			</div>
			<div class="form-group has-feedback">
				{{mdl-textfield label='Number of additional guests?' value=guestsValue type="number"}}
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-offset-3 col-sm-6">
				{{mdl-button isRaised=true text='Add Guest' action='addGuest' disabled=isNotValid}}
			</div>
		</div>
		<br><hr><br>
		<h1>Your Guest List</h1>
		<p>Once you have some guests, you can now manage and view them.<br>All the guests will be listed in a table and you can can <strong>RSVP or remove them.</strong></p>
	    <div class="form-group">
			{{#link-to 'index.mywedding.guests'}}{{mdl-button isRaised=true text='Guest List'}}{{/link-to}}
		</div>
		<br>
	</div>

	<div class="" style=" padding:10px 20px 60px 20px">
